title: Wall Street Breakfast April 22: Fed will Hike Rates by 75 Basis Points in June and July
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: A relentlessly hawkish Federal Reserve is ramping up market expectations for big interest rate hikes. The Department of Energy said Thursday it awarded 12 contracts for 30M barrels of oil from the SPR. Disney stock finds new low as Florida approves ending special tax district. Check out the WSB article here.
